      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait 50mg of lorazepam?? that sounds like a lot. i've never taken that before. and is the aspirin actually gonna help with the chest pain or is it just for the clotting thing? i really don't want to go to a hospital in a foreign country if i can just deal with this at the hotel.",
